Step 4: Test the Extension  
To test the extension, you can load it into Chrome's extension manager and navigate to an Amazon page. The extension should display the generated prices to you.

Step 5: Deploy the Extension  
Once you're happy with the extension, you can deploy it to your online store. You'll need to provide users with instructions on how to install the extension and connect it to their Amazon profiles.

